def: The act or process of devitrifying, or the state of beingdevitrified. Specifically, the conversion of molten glassy matterinto a stony mass by slow cooling, the result being the formation ofcrystallites, microbites, etc., in the glassy base, which are thencalled devitrification products.
The quality of being queenly; the; characteristic of a queen;stateliness; eminence among women in attractions or power.
Motion on foot; progress in walking. [Obs.]The incession or local motion of animals. Sir T. Browne.
An inference which does not follow from the premises.
Having made journeys; having gained knowledge or experience bytraveling; hence, knowing; experienced. [Written also travelled.]The traveled thane, Athenian Aberdeen. Byron.
A word consisting of twelve syllables.
Shooting at pigeons liberated, or glass balls or clay pigeonssprung into the air, from a trap. -- Trap shooter.
In an ornate manner. Sir T. More.
